OL,3,CJustice Secretary dubs assisted dying
OL,4,CBill 'path to death on demand'
OL,6,FThe state should "never offer death as
OL,7,Fa service", the Justice Secretary has
OL,8,Fsaid, in a strongly worded
OL,9,Fintervention over the assisted dying
OL,10,FBill ahead of a historic Commons vote
OL,11,Fnext week.
OL,13,FIn a letter to constituents, Shabana
OL,14,FMahmood said she was "profoundly
OL,15,Fconcerned" by the legislation, not
OL,16,Fjust for religious reasons but because
OL,17,Fit could create a "slippery slope
OL,18,Ftowards death on demand", the Observer
OL,19,Freported.
