OL,6,FMs Mahmood has previously made clear
OL,7,Fshe would vote against the Bill
OL,8,Falongside Health Secretary Wes
OL,9,FStreeting, who faced a backlash after
OL,10,Fsuggesting the changes would cost the
OL,11,FNHS more.
OL,13,FBut her letter to voters goes further,
OL,14,Fstating: "Sadly, recent scandals `
OL,15,Fsuch as Hillsborough, infected blood
OL,16,Fand the Post Office Horizon ` have
OL,17,Freminded us that the state and those
OL,18,Facting on its behalf are not always
OL,19,Fbenign.
