OL,6,FIt would also make coercion an offence
OL,7,Fwith a possible punishment of 14 years
OL,8,Fin jail.
OL,10,FThe Bill, which covers England and
OL,11,FWales, states only terminally ill
OL,12,Fadults with under six months left to
OL,13,Flive and a settled wish to die would
OL,14,Fbe eligible.
